-- Ceradyne gets 5-year order to supply body armor to U.S. military
-- 
-- Fri Jan 4, 2008 7:56am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/04/businesspro-ceradyne-order-dc-idUSWNAS563620080104

 

 (Reuters) - Ceramics maker Ceradyne Inc CRDN.O said it 
received an order from the United States Special Operations 
Command for supplying body armor with a maximum contract value 
in excess of $400 million. 

  The initial delivery for the five-year indefinite 
delivery/indefinite quantity contract is worth $4.9 million and 
is scheduled for early 2008, the company said in a statement.  (Reporting by Anant Vijay Kala in Bangalore; Editing by 
Anthony Kurian)